item.title: Bonus Episode: I Tried the Gateway Meditations..
item.description: In 2003, a declassified document released by the CIA detailed the observation of the Gateway Tapes, a process created by The Monroe Institute in the 1980s. The series of guided meditations used hemi-sync technology to synchronize the brain's hemispheres, facilitating altered states of consciousness. Participants reported experiences ranging from deep relaxation and heightened creativity to out-of-body experiences and expanded awareness... item.title: Episode 845 John At Disney World & Eagles Super Sunday!
item.description: Hello everybody and welcome to the WDW Mainstreet podcast. Pull up your stool with John and Doug as they discuss all of the latest news from around Walt Disney World and their worlds. Doug starts the show off with his excitement for his Birds in the Superbowl. John had a two-night stay at the Boardwalk and believe it or not he went to EPCOT both days and enjoyed multiple food option from this year's Festival Of The Arts...
